Insider Activity


Individual




Ernest Scott Santi



Mr. Ernest S. Santi is Independent Director at W.W. Grainger, Inc., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Illinois Tool Works, Inc., and Secretary & Trustee at Ravinia Festival Association. He is on the Board of Directors at W.W. Grainger, Inc., Illinois Tool Works, Inc., Ravinia Festival Association, Mapi, Inc., The Museum of Science & Industry, Chicago Symphony Orchestra Association, Rush University Medical Center, and Junior Achievement of Chicago.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Illinois and an MBA from the Kellogg School of Management.



